  <%= image_tag '/fit_8.png', class: "mt-4 ml-4 mb-5" %>

  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1%; margin-top: 8%; font-weight: 700;">04</h3>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 2%; font-weight: 700;">"주간 리포트"</h4>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 6%; font-weight: 400;">한 주간의 <strong>종합 평가,</strong></h4>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 1%; font-weight: 400;"><strong>식사 트렌드, 운동피드백, 목표달성률,</strong></h4>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 1%; font-weight: 400;"><strong>코치의 종합 피드백</strong>이 담긴</h4>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 1%; font-weight: 400;">위클리 리포트를 보내드려요.</h4>
  <%= image_tag '/fit_9.png', class: "mt-4 ml-4 mb-5" %>

  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1%; margin-top: 8%; font-weight: 700;">05</h3>
  <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0%; margin-top: 2%; font-weight: 700;">무제한 Q&A 세션</h4>
